<head>SHADE</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">陰蔭處</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>PLACE LACKING LIGHT of SUN SURROUNDED BY PLACES WITH LIGHT OF SUN.</p>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. he general area of shade is yīn 陰 (ant. guāng 光 "light")</p>
<p>2. Yīn 蔭 refers specifically to the shadow of a tree.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
